name: pensive
description: there is a turmoil, and psychological rejection in the expression of the characters made, every human being will stop at a certain point, and rethink what is the purpose of what he has done during his life, what is the end? in the brain will be crowded with various questions, humans live with various characteristics and the past, the turning point of a person will determine his future life goals, the painting emphasizes the disclosure of psychological problems, adversity and all past bad deeds, depicted with one figure with confused expression and many eyeballs on the side, symbolizing the anxiety of pain, there is a desire to go and change life for the better
